Entries.default: "For what do you come to see us, outsider?"
"Ekera, the islands are restless of late."
"Speak to Ruāsare. I cannot help you."
"Ruāsare said you can stay? Cause no trouble."
"We dream of lost Ukaizo. Do you dream, outsider?"
"I have eaten enough koīki to turn my leavings red. Ekera, it is enough."
"The son of Ngati? We are honored."
"Your bird friend, her plumage is very fine."
